              "value": "Link the pairs of sentences using the connectors in brackets. Make\nthe necessary changes.\na. The Arabs conquered many rich provinces. They became\npowerful. (after)\nb. Some of the governors were corrupt. Their reign didn't\nlast long. (so...that)\nc. The two brothers got into a fight. They lost their\nsovereignty. (if)"
